$:/language/Buttons/Mark/New/Text.text:
Marking code (CSS) prefixed by @@, e.g: @@background-color:Cyan;

The closing @@ will be added automatically upon applying.

Remember to add a descriptive title in the caption field!

$:/xp/mark-button/color.css.text:
/*
 * 快速标记「标题」和「列表」的颜色
 */

.red,
.r {
    color: red;
    fill: red;
}

.green,
.g {
    color: green;
    fill: green;
}

.blue,
.b {
    color: blue;
    fill: blue;
}

.orange,
.o {
    color: orange;
    fill: orange;
}

.purple,
.p {
    color: purple;
    fill: purple;
}

.violet,
.v {
    color: violet;
    fill: violet;
}
